Solution:
The projection of $\begin{pmatrix} 4 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix}$ onto $\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}$ is of the form $k \begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}$ for some scalar $k.$  This projection is the closest vector to $\begin{pmatrix} 4 \\ 5 \end{pmatrix}$ that lies on the line spanned by $\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}.$

[asy]
